cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SD, cs.DL 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as it discusses the collection and analysis of social media data from Reddit. It may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it discusses computational tools for searching and aggregating data. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it discusses the impact of social media data on scientific research. It may also fall under cs.SD (Software Development) as it discusses the development of a platform for data collection and analysis. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.DL (Machine Learning) as machine learning techniques are often used in social media analysis.
